title: Bob Dylan's Theme Time Radio Hour: Kiss (320Kbps MP3)
description:
On Feb 11, 2015, German radio station "radioins" aired this previously un-aired episode of Bob Dylan's SiriusXM radio program, Theme Time Radio Hour, with the theme "Kiss."  Here's a tracklisting of the songs: 

1. The Shoop Shoop Song (It's in His Kiss) - Betty Everett
2. Always Late with Your Kisses - Lefty Frizzell
3. Passionate Kisses - Lucinda Williams
4. Kiss - Prince
5. Kissing in the Dark - Memphis Minnie
6. Kiss Tomorrow Goodbye - Danny White
7. Pucker Paint - Huelyn Duvall
8. Lipstick on Your Collar - Connie Francis
9. 'Til I Kissed You - The Everly Brothers
10. Let's Kiss and Make Up - The Falcons
11. One More Time - Roy Head and The Traits
12. Last Kiss - J. Frank Wilson and the Cavaliers
13. A Kiss to Build a Dream On - Louis Armstrong

Link to the radioins page: http://www.radioeins.de/themen/musik/freundliche-uebernahme/musiker/bob-dylan---theme-time-radio-hour-kiss-show.html
